file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  contact:
    email: support@igeolise.com
    name: API Support
  termsOfService: https://www.traveltime.com/terms-and-conditions
  title: TravelTime API
  version: 1.2.3
externalDocs:
  url: http://docs.traveltime.com
servers:
- url: https://api.traveltimeapp.com
security:
- ApplicationId: []
  ApiKey: []
paths:
  /v4/time-filter:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/time-filter
      operationId: timeFilter
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/TimeFilter'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeFilter'
          description: Given origin and destination points filter out points that
            cannot be reached within specified time limit. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/time-filter)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/time-filter/postcodes:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/postcode-search
      operationId: timeFilterPostcodes
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/TimeFilterPostcodes'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeFilterPostcodes'
          description: Find reachable postcodes from origin and get statistics about
            such postcodes. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/postcode-search/)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/time-filter/postcode-districts:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/postcode-search
      operationId: timeFilterPostcodeDistricts
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/TimeFilterPostcodeDistricts'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeFilterPostcodeDistricts'
          description: Find districts that have a certain coverage from origin and
            get statistics about postcodes within such districts. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/postcode-district-filter/)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/time-filter/postcode-sectors:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/postcode-sector-filter
      operationId: timeFilterPostcodeSectors
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/TimeFilterPostcodeSectors'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeFilterPostcodeSectors'
          description: Find sectors that have a certain coverage from origin and get
            statistics about postcodes within such sectors. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/postcode-sector-filter/)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/time-filter/fast:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/time-filter-fast
      operationId: timeFilterFast
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/TimeFilterFast'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeFilterFast'
          description: A very fast version of Time Filter. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/time-filter-fast/)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/time-map:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/time-map
      operationId: timeMap
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/TimeMap'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeMap'
            application/vnd.wkt+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeMapWkt'
            application/vnd.wkt-no-holes+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeMapWkt'
            application/vnd.bounding-boxes+json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeMapBoundingBoxes'
          description: Given origin coordinates, find shapes of zones reachable within
            corresponding travel time. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/time-map/)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/routes:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/routes
      operationId: routes
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/Routes'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseRoutes'
          description: Returns routing information between source and destinations.
            [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/routes/)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/geocoding/search:
    get:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/geocoding-search
      operationId: geocodingSearch
      parameters:
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: query
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: focus.lat
        required: false
        schema:
          format: double
          type: number
        style: form
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: focus.lng
        required: false
        schema:
          format: double
          type: number
        style: form
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: within.country
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: form
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseGeocoding'
          description: Match a query string to geographic coordinates. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/geocoding-search/)
        default:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseError'
          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)
      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/geocoding/reverse:
    get:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/geocoding-reverse
      operationId: geocodingReverseSearch
      parameters:
      - explode: true
        in: query
        name: lat
        required: true
        schema:

          type: number
        style: form
      - explode: true

        name: lng
        required: true
        schema:
          format: double
          type: number
        style: form
      - explode: true

        style: form
      responses:

            application/json:

        default:

  /v4/map-info:

      x-eov-operation-handler: controllers/DefaultController
  /v4/supported-locations:
    post:
      externalDocs:
        url: http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/supported-locations
      operationId: supportedLocations
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/SupportedLocations'
      responses:
        "200":
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseSupportedLocations'
          description: Find out what points are supported by our api. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/supported-locations/)

          description: The json body returned upon error. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/error-response)

    GeocodingReverseLng:

    TimeFilterPostcodeDistricts:

      required: true
    TimeFilterPostcodeSectors:

      required: true
    TimeFilterFast:

      required: true
    Routes:

        application/json:

      required: true
    TimeMap:

        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/RequestTimeMap'
      required: true
    SupportedLocations:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/RequestSupportedLocations'
      required: true

        application/json:
          schema:

      description: Match a query string to geographic coordinates. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/geocoding-search/)
    TimeMap:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeMap'
        application/vnd.wkt+json:
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ResponseTimeMapWkt'
        application/vnd.wkt-no-holes+json:

        application/vnd.bounding-boxes+json:

      description: Find out what points are supported by our api. [Docs link](http://docs.traveltime.com/reference/supported-locations/)

      example:
        lng: 3.616076749251911
        lat: 9.301444243932576
      properties:
        lat:
          format: double
          type: number
        lng:
          format: double
          type: number

      - lat
      - lng
      type: object

      type: string
    RequestDepartureArrivalLocationOne:
      type: string
    RequestTravelTime:

      type: integer
    RequestDepartureArrivalTime:

    ResponseLocalTime:
      type: string
    RequestRoutesProperty:
